dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Topatopa Mountains quadrangle, Ventura County, California
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr.; edited by Helmut E. Ehrenspeck.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Prepared in cooperation with the U.S. Forest Service, Los Padres National Forest; California Department of Conservation, Division of Mines and Geology; and U.S. Geological Survey."
Includes 2 col. cross sections, acknowledgements, index to sources of geology, age correlation chart and location map.
